title: Ad Infinitum - Official Maw of Madness Trailer | gamescom 2023 (Warning: Flashing Lights)
description:
Warning: The trailer has rapid, flashing lights.

See the twisted world and the terrors that await you in this latest creepy trailer for the upcoming psychological horror game Ad Infinitum. 

When reality is a nightmare, nightmares become real. Will you escape the maw of madness? Trapped between two realities, you play a younger German soldier and wander through a vast mansion and the trenches of WW1 where you must fend off the terrible creatures that are coming after you in Ad Infinitum.

Ad Infinitum will be available on PC, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X/S on September 14, 2023.

description:

title: FULL AMD Stage Presentation (RX 7800 XT 16GB & FSR3) | gamescom 2023
description:
AMD presents the RX 7800 XT 16GB and FSR 3. 
The RX 7800 XT 16GB and RX 7700 XT 12GB GPUs are the latest in the RX 7000 series of graphics cards, significantly improving the graphical performance of the latest PC games.
FSR 3 is a follow-up to FSR 2 that, as its name suggests, triples the frame rate fidelity of your favorite PC titles.

title: Off the Grid - Official Gameplay Trailer | gamescom 2023
description:
Check out the first gameplay trailer for Off The Grid, a new battle royale third-person shooter directed by Neill Blomkamp (District 9). 

Off The Grid throws players into a covert corporate war between three companies on the tropical, dystopian Teardrop Island. Blending PvE and PvP, you’ll experience hectic 150-player battle royales as a cyberlimbed Zero, fighting to survive while simultaneously taking on a 60-hour narrative campaign. Extract high-value loot and upgrade your body with cybernetic limbs to give yourself the edge to reach the top.

#IGN #Gaming #OffTheGrid

New weapons have also been added like the Rocket Ram for clearing out enemy builds, the new Infiltrator Pump Shotgun, and more. Fortnite Chapter 4 Season 4 is available now.

title: Banishers: Ghosts of New Eden - The First Preview | gamescom 2023
description:
At a glance, Banishers: Ghosts of New Eden owes a lot to Sony’s recent God of War outings. Its close third-person camera perspective, linear-but-open level design, and mix of environmental puzzles and hard-hitting melee combat are all present. But there’s more than meets the eye here. After playing a whole quest I’ve discovered that beneath that surface lies a soul just as connected to the Life is Strange series developer Don't Nod is famed for as it is to Sony’s godly behemoth.

#IGN #Gaming #gamescom

title: Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 - Official 14 Minutes of Gameplay | gamescom 2023
description:
Watch 14 minutes of exciting new Warhammer 40K: Space Marine 2 gameplay. Get a look at an epic battle that takes place in a perilous swamp as you assist the Cadians on the battlefield, using a variety of destructive weapons and abilities at the Space Marine's disposal. Then head through an enemy base, before securing the facility. 

Prepare to unleash your deadly abilities and use your arsenal of devastating weaponry to obliterate the relentless Tyranid hordes. Uncover dark secrets and take on the horrors of the galaxy in huge battles on faraway planets as you prove your loyalty to humanity. The galaxy is in peril, entire worlds are falling, and The Imperium needs you. Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 is coming to PS5, Xbox Series X/S, and PC in Winter 2023.

#IGN #Gaming #Warhammer

title: Armored Core 6 Performance Review - PS5 vs Xbox Series X|S vs PS4 vs Steam Deck
description:
Armored Core 6 performance on the PS5 and Xbox Series X|S has been put through the paces and our findings of this From Software favourite are not to be missed. Armored Core 6 is a return to the series roots with a cross gen PC and console option that many will love. We test the PS5, Xbox Series X|S and even the Steam Deck against each other to see how they all run in this Armored Core 6 Performance Review.

Chapters
0:00 Introduction & Contents
0:45 PS5 vs Series X Visual comparisons & modes including Ray Tracing
3:50 Series S modes and comparison to PS5, Series X & Last gen PS4
5:39 Steam Deck Summary
6:05 Performance testing - PS5, Series X|S, PS4, Steam Deck
12:21 Summary

GTA 6 Leaker Hacked Rockstar Using An Amazon Fire Stick - IGN Daily Fix
description: In today's Daily Fix: a British court convicted a teenager associated with the hacking group Lapsus$ for his role in the massive leak of unreleased Grand Theft Auto 6 assets stolen from Rockstar. The hacker's youth didn't stop him from accessing the systems of other companies like Nvidia and Uber - he was even out on bail for one of those hacks when he was arrested for the GTA 6 leak! More on that, plus Mortal Kombat ko-kreator Ed Boon reassures IGN's audience that DLC fighters Homelander and Omni-Man, each a riff on the "evil Superman" archetype, will have totally different movesets in the upcoming Mortal Kombat 1.

title: Eternights - Official Release Date Update Trailer | gamescom 2023
description:
Eternights will be available on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Steam, and the Epic Games Store on September 12, 2023. Check out the latest trailer to see gameplay, fierce enemies, and more from Eternights, the upcoming game that is a blend of dating and monster slaying.

In Eternights, the world we know is turned upside down when a mysterious event transforms people into violent monsters and creates giant walls that close in your city. When your arm is replaced with a magical, shapeshifting replica that grants you strange powers, it’s up to you to break through the wall and save the world… and your love life. Dates still happen during the apocalypse, and even when a surreal evil brings life as you know it crashing down, what matters most is the people around you.

#IGN #Gaming
